oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Sister Mary Cecelia and Students
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Students; Nuns; Women
oai_dc:dc.dc:description:
Sister Mary Cecelia posed with students of St. Agnes Academy. At this time, the Catholic girls' school was located at Vance and Orleans in downtown Memphis.
St. Agnes collaborated with Christian Brothers High School and College over the years.
